Sentencas: Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC)-impregnated La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 (LSM) composite cathodes were fabricated on anode-supported yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) thin films.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: Electrochemical performances of the solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) were investigated in the present study.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: Four single cells, i.e., Cell-1, Cell-2, Cell-3 and Cell-4 were obtained after the fabrication of four different cathodes, i.e., pure LSM and SDC/LSM composites in the weight ratios of 25/75, 36/64 and 42/58, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: Impedance spectra under open-circuit conditions showed that the cathode performance was gradually improved with the increasing SDC loading.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: Similarly, the maximum power densities (MPD) of the four cells were increased with the SDC amount below 700 degrees C. Whereas, the cell performance of Cell-4 was lower than that of Cell-3 at 800 degrees C, arising from the increased concentration polarization at high current densities.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: This was caused by the lowered porosity with the impregnation cycle.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: This disadvantage could be suppressed by lowering the operating temperature or by increasing the oxygen concentration at the cathode side.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: The ratio of electrode polarization loss in the total voltage drop versus current density showed that the cell performance was primarily determined by the electrode polarization.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: The contribution of the ohmic resistance was increased when the operating temperature was lowered.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: When a 100 ml min(-1) oxygen flow was introduced to the cathode side, Cell-3 produced MPDs of 1905, 1587 and 1179 mW cm(-2) at 800, 750 and 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs

Sentencas: The high cell outputs demonstrated the merits of the novel and effective SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes.
Titulo: Effect of SDC-impregnated LSM cathodes on the performance of anode-supported YSZ films for SOFCs
